<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الْحَاقَّةُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> مَا الْحَاقَّةُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا الْحَاقَّةُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> كَذَّبَتْ ثَمُودُ وَعَادٌ بِالْقَارِعَةِ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>